# Password Manager V2

Password Manager V2 is a secure web-based password management application developed using Flask, SQLite, HTML, CSS, and Python. The application enables users to create accounts, securely store passwords, and manage their credentials through an ocean-inspired interface.

## Features

* User Registration and Login
* Secure Password Storage
* SQLite Database Integration
* Password Viewing and Management
* Ocean-Themed User Interface
* Flask Backend Architecture

## Technologies Used

* Python
* Flask
* SQLite
* HTML5
* CSS3

## Project Goal

To provide a simple and secure password management solution while demonstrating full-stack web development concepts using Flask.
